<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT48">
<l>vēṅkaṭamē viṇṇōr toḻuvatuvu meymmaiyāl</l>
<l>vēṅkaṭamē meyviṉaiṉōy tīrppatuvum vēṅkaṭamē</l>
<l>tāṉavarai vīḻattaṉ ṉāḻip paṭaitoṭṭu</l>
<l>vāṉavaraik kāppāṉ malai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Veṅkaṭam is [the mountain] that the celestials worship truth[fully].</l>
<l>Veṅkaṭam is [the mountain] that ends the disease of bodily troubles.</l>
<l>Veṅkaṭam is the mountain of [the Lord] who protects the celestials</l>
<l>using His discus-weapon so that the Rakshasas fall.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
